<script>
    $tudio('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl04_divModuleContainer').q4News({
        category: '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000',
        tags: [""],

        limit: 3,
        tagSelect: '#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl04_selectEvergreenNewsTag',
        tagTrigger: '._ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl04_divModuleContainer_evergreen-tag-trigger',

        useMoment: true,
        dateFormat: {"date":"MMMM D, YYYY","time":"h:mm A "},
        showAllYears: true,
        fetchAllYears: true,
        yearSelect: '#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl04_selectEvergreenNewsYear',
        yearContainer: '#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl04_selectEvergreenNewsYear',
        yearTemplate: '<option value="{{value}}">{{ year }}</option>',
        noYearsMessage: '<option value="-">-</option>',
        allYearsText: 'All',

        itemNotFoundMessage: $tudio('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl04_divModuleContainertplEvergreenNewsNoItems').html(),
        loadingMessage: $tudio("#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl04_divModuleContainertplEvergreenNewsLoading").html(),

        itemContainer: '#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl04_divNewsItemsContainer',
        itemTemplate: $tudio('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl04_divModuleContainertplListEvergreenNews').html(),

        loadShortBody: 0,
        shortBodyLength: 240,

        itemsComplete: function (e) {
            if ($tudio(e.target).find('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl04_divModuleContainerdivEvergreenNewsStatusAnnouncement').length) {
                var year = $tudio(e.target).find('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl04_selectEvergreenNewsYear').val();
                var tag = $tudio(e.target).find('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl04_selectEvergreenNewsTag').val();

                $tudio('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl04_divModuleContainerdivEvergreenNewsStatusAnnouncement').text('Showing ' + (year === '-1' ? 'All ' : year + ' ') + tag + ' News');
            }
            if ($tudio(e.target).find('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl04_navNewsPager').length) {
                $tudio(e.target).find('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl04_navNewsPager').q4Pager({
                    content: $tudio(e.target).find('.evergreen-news-item'),
                    perPage: 0,
                    showPrevNext: false,
                });
            }
        },

        complete: function (e) {
            if ($tudio('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl04_divEvergreenNewsFilter').length) {
                $tudio(e.target).find('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl04_divModuleContainerdivEvergreenNewsStatusAnnouncement').remove();
                q4EvergreenHelpers.a11yAnnouncement('polite', '_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl04_divModuleContainerdivEvergreenNewsStatusAnnouncement', $tudio(e.target).find('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl04_divEvergreenNewsFilter'), function (el) {
                    var year = $tudio(e.target).find('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl04_selectEvergreenNewsYear').val();
                    var tag = $tudio(e.target).find('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl04_selectEvergreenNewsTag').val();

                    $tudio(el).text('Showing ' + (year === '-1' ? 'All ' : year + ' ') + tag + ' News');
                });
            }

            if (0 == 2) {
                var containerClassName = ".evergreen-container.evergreen-container--outer.evergreen-container--news";

                function checkContainerHeight() {
                    var windowWidth = $(window).outerWidth();
                    var bgContainer = $tudio(e.target).find(".evergreen-news-layout-overlay-background");
                    var newsContainer = $tudio(e.target).find(containerClassName);
                    var newsContainerSpaceClass = "evergreen-container-news--overlay-space";

                    if (windowWidth <= 768 && windowWidth > 480 ) {
                        if (newsContainer.outerHeight() > bgContainer.outerHeight()) {
                            newsContainer.addClass(newsContainerSpaceClass);
                        } else {
                            newsContainer.removeClass(newsContainerSpaceClass);
                        }
                    } else {
                        newsContainer.removeClass(newsContainerSpaceClass);
                    }
                }

                checkContainerHeight();

                $(window).resize(function () {
                    checkContainerHeight();
                });

                var observer = new MutationObserver(function (mutationsList, observer) {
                    for (var mutation of mutationsList) {
                        if (mutation.type === 'childList' || mutation.type === 'subtree') {
                            checkContainerHeight();
                            break;
                        }
                    }
                });

                observer.observe($tudio(e.target).find(containerClassName)[0], { subtree: true, childList: true });
            }
        }
    });
</script>

<script>
    $tudio('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl07_divModuleContainer').q4Events({
        showFuture: true,
        showPast: true,
        limit: 3,
        fetchAllYears: true,
        useMoment: true,
        dateFormat: {"date":"MMMM D, YYYY","time":"h:mm A "},
        tags: [""],
        showAllYears: true,
        sortAscending: false,
        yearContainer: '#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl07_selectEvergreenEventYear',
        yearTemplate: '<option value="{{value}}">{{ year }}</option>',
        yearSelect: '#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl07_selectEvergreenEventYear',
        itemNotFoundMessage: $tudio('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl07_divModuleContainertplEvergreenEventNoItems').html(),
        loadingMessage: $tudio("#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl07_divModuleContainertplEvergreenEventLoading").html(),
        itemContainer: '#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl07_divEventItemsContainer',
        itemTemplate: $tudio('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl07_divModuleContainertplEvergreenEvent').html(),
        itemsComplete: function (e) {
            q4EvergreenHelpers.addToCalendar($tudio(e.target).find('.evergreen-event-add-to-calendar'));
            if ($tudio(e.target).find('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl07_divModuleContainerdivEvergreenEventStatusAnnouncement').length) {
                var value = $tudio(e.target).find('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl07_selectEvergreenEventYear').val();
                $tudio('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl07_divModuleContainerdivEvergreenEventStatusAnnouncement').text('Showing events from year ' + (value === '-1' ? 'All' : value));

            }
            if ($tudio(e.target).find('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl07_navEventPager').length) {
                $tudio(e.target).find('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl07_navEventPager').q4Pager({
                    content: $tudio(e.target).find('.evergreen-event-item'),
                    perPage: 0,
                    showPrevNext: false,
                });
            }
        },
        complete: function (e) {
            if ($tudio('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl07_divEvergreenEventFilter').length) {
                $tudio(e.target).find('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl07_divModuleContainerdivEvergreenEventStatusAnnouncement').remove();
                q4EvergreenHelpers.a11yAnnouncement('polite', '_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl07_divModuleContainerdivEvergreenEventStatusAnnouncement', $tudio(e.target).find('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl07_divEvergreenEventFilter'), function (el) {
                    var value = $tudio(e.target).find('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl07_selectEvergreenEventYear').val();
                    $tudio(el).text('Showing events from year ' + (value === '-1' ? 'All' : value));
                });

                if ($tudio('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl07_divEvergreenEventYearTabContainer').length) {
                    function toggleTab(e, type) {
                        $tudio(e.target).closest('.evergreen-tabs').find('a').removeClass('evergreen--selected');
                        $tudio(e.target).addClass("evergreen--selected");
                        $tudio('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl07_divModuleContainer').q4Events(type);
                    }

                    $tudio('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl07_hrefEvergreenEventUpcomingTab').off().on('click', function (e) {
                        toggleTab(e, 'setShowFuture');
                    });
                    $tudio('#_ctrl0_ContentPane-home-news-events_ctl07_hrefEvergreenEventPastTab').off().on('click', function (e) {
                        toggleTab(e, 'setShowPast');
                    })
                }
            }
        }
    });
</script>

<script>
    function showMessage(message, targetElementId = "_ctrl0_FooterPane-footer-pane-main_ctl10_divMailingListMessage") {
        $("#" + targetElementId).text(message);
        $("#" + targetElementId).show();
    }

    function getCookie(name) {
        var nameEQ = name + "=";
        var ca = document.cookie.split(";");
        for (var i = 0; i < ca.length; i++) {
            var c = ca[i];
            while (c.charAt(0) == " ") c = c.substring(1, c.length);
            if (c.indexOf(nameEQ) == 0) return c.substring(nameEQ.length, c.length);
        }
        return null;
    }

    // see STD-647
    (async function () {
        const q4lTriggerClientID = window.localStorage.getItem("q4l_trigger_clientID");
        // we check q4lTriggerClientID so that when there are multiple mailing lists,
        // only the one that the user submitted will have its view changed so there is
        // a cleaner UX
        const didTriggerFlow = q4lTriggerClientID === "_ctrl0_FooterPane-footer-pane-main_ctl10";
        let idToken = window.location.hash.includes("id_token") ? window.location.hash.replace("#id_token=", "") : null;
        idToken = idToken ?? getCookie(Q4Login.StorageKeys.SessionToken);
        if (window.location.hash.includes("error")) {
            const errorCode = window.location.hash.replace("#error=", "");
            if (errorCode === "401.1" && didTriggerFlow) {
                const message = "Your email is not verified. Please click the verification link we sent to your inbox.";
                $("#_ctrl0_FooterPane-footer-pane-main_ctl10_divModuleContainer").hide();
                showMessage(message);
            }
        }
        else if (window.location.hash.includes("message")) {
            const message = decodeURIComponent(window.location.hash.replace("#message=", ""));
            if (didTriggerFlow) {
                showMessage(message, "_ctrl0_FooterPane-footer-pane-main_ctl10_validationsummary");
            }
        }
        else if (idToken) {
            // default message
            let message = "Unable to subscribe using your Q4 Account, please try again.";
            const mailingListSelections = localStorage.getItem("q4l_mailing_selections");
            if (!!mailingListSelections && didTriggerFlow) {
                try {
                    // hide mailing list selections, then show spinner
                    $("#_ctrl0_FooterPane-footer-pane-main_ctl10_divModuleContainer").hide();
                    $("#_ctrl0_FooterPane-footer-pane-main_ctl11-spinner").show();

                    // build and make request
                    const requestOptions = {
                        method: "PUT",
                        headers: {
                            "Content-Type": "application/json",
                            "Authorization": "Bearer " + idToken
                        },
                        body: mailingListSelections
                    };
                    const publicApi = "https://gitlab2024ir.studio.q4api.com/api/MailingList";
                    const response = await fetch(publicApi, requestOptions)
                        .catch(error => console.log(error));
                    const subscribeResult = await response.json();
                    if (subscribeResult) {
                        message = subscribeResult.data;
                    }
                }
                catch (ex) {
                    console.log(ex);
                }
                localStorage.removeItem("q4l_mailing_selections");
                localStorage.removeItem("q4l_email");
                // set the output message then show it
                showMessage(message);
            }
            else if (window.location.hash.includes("id_token") && !mailingListSelections && didTriggerFlow) {
                // if there is no mailing list selections at this point, then
                // something is up.
                showMessage(message);
            }
        }

        // clean up
        $("#_ctrl0_FooterPane-footer-pane-main_ctl11-spinner").hide();
    })();
</script></div></div></div></div>
